{"tid":1227294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反送中] 希望各位珍惜生命，林鄭唔值得你為佢而死","createTime":"2019-06-15T14:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T03:11:04.000Z","uid":52658,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fbac9234a9eeeed635adba0d08e454c68ca7187b","tid":1227294,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:50:09.000Z","msg":"今次呢件事可能會引發自殺效應<br />\n但我想奉勸各位珍惜生命各位<br />\n要留返有用之軀 <br />\n同呢個垃圾政權對抗對底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好心痛 無晒心機<br />\n咁就有位大好青年過左身..<br />\n希望果位烈士RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林鄭月娥 <br />\n你條柒婆不惜犧牲香港前途 換取自己既政治仕途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等你老母比天收</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c8eec7a36c55990d778b6d3425d18d8238e32a2d","tid":1227294,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要求取消佢外國護照單野搞成點</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c35335acf4f703c90a10bfbe8d3b2a369e7fa6ef","tid":1227294,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680a77741ea80a035747ea1ec2f590120d3817df","tid":1227294,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c044e7357b9b037958b92c3fb37b53a961818645","tid":1227294,"uid":52175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:18:30.000Z","msg":"希望義士rip<br />\n希望其他人好好保重自己<br />\n因為抗爭未完  香港仍然需要大家繼續出力<br />\n更希望義士啲犧牲唔係白費  <br />\n可以喚醒沉默嘅香港人 走出嚟一齊抗惡法<br />\n可以喚醒垃圾建制派嘅良知  唔好盲目支持政府<br />\n<br />\n我無宗教信仰  但啱啱都祈左禱 如果真係有天堂 希望義士可以係天堂睇住  同我地一齊守護香港<br />\n<br />\n心情沉重  Sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"f30f841a2c9ac5b0b8d9376054361417b3e1d906","tid":1227294,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:20:50.000Z","msg":"唉 <br />\n大家冷靜"},{"pid":"9b3cd72ab4fb42140e5818a5a1faf08f2bf05552","tid":1227294,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}